<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1608089-i-really-wanted-to-love-this-book-but-the">I really wanted to love this book, but the historical inaccuracies and the imposition of modern-day standards onto historical characters made me quite dislike it. Does the rest of the series improve? I love the premise, but I need the execution to be there too.</a>
</div>
